# UI/UX Conventions

## Layout

- The app shell (`AppShell`) provides `max-w-7xl` centering, `py-8 pb-24` padding, and scrolling via `overflow-y-auto` on `<main>`.
- `html` and `body` have `overflow: hidden; height: 100%` — never rely on body scroll.
- Pages render inside the shell; don't add their own max-width or horizontal padding.

## Typography

- Page titles: `text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900` (via `PageHeader`)
- Subtitles: `text-sm text-gray-600` (via `PageHeader`)
- Section headings: `text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900`
- Form labels: `text-sm font-medium text-gray-700`

## Cards

- Form/control cards: `rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-xs`
- Content/display cards: `rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-xs`
- Error cards: use `<ErrorCard>` from `@/components/resource-form-header`

## Primary Buttons

- Solid: `bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-xs`
- Disabled: `disabled:bg-primary-300`
- Link variant: use `PrimaryLinkButton` from `@/components/page-header`
- Submit variant: use `PrimaryButton` from `@/components/page-header`

## Forms

- Place save/create buttons in the `PageHeader` actions slot (top-right), not in sticky footers.
- Use `ResourceFormHeader` for name/description fields on all resource forms.
- Use `ErrorCard` for all error messages.
- Never use `fixed`/`sticky` bottom bars for save actions.

## Shared Components

| Component | Import | Purpose |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| `PageHeader` | `@/components/page-header` | All page titles, back links, actions |
| `PrimaryLinkButton` | `@/components/page-header` | Navigation CTAs with plus icon |
| `PrimaryButton` | `@/components/page-header` | Form submit buttons with loading |
| `ResourceFormHeader` | `@/components/resource-form-header` | Name + Description card for any resource |
| `ErrorCard` | `@/components/resource-form-header` | Error messages in red card |
| `DataTable` | `@/components/data-table` | Generic typed table with sticky toolbar, infinite scroll, loading/empty states |
| `useInfiniteList` | `@/hooks/use-infinite-list` | Hook for backend-powered search, pagination accumulation, and infinite scroll |
| `SearchBar` | `@/components/data-table` | Search input for DataTable toolbar (backend-powered) |
| `SelectAllCheckbox` | `@/components/data-table` | Toolbar checkbox with count label and indeterminate state |
| `FilterPills` | `@/components/data-table` | Toolbar pill buttons for backend-driven status filtering |
| `NameCell` | `@/components/data-table` | Linked name + subtitle for table rows |
| `StatusBadge` | `@/components/data-table` | Consistent active/inactive/deleted pill |
| `DateCell` | `@/components/data-table` | Formatted date for table rows |
| `checkboxColumn` | `@/components/data-table` | Factory for bulk-select checkbox column |
| `actionsColumn` | `@/components/data-table` | Factory for declarative action columns (icon + label + onClick) |
| `BulkDeleteBar` | `@/components/bulk-delete-bar` | Floating bar for bulk selection actions |
